OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FA man accused of sexually abusing an
OL,7,Fadopted baby allegedly murdered by his
OL,8,Fpartner told a jury he never saw
OL,9,Fanyone harm the child and he trusted
OL,10,Fhis co-accused.
OL,12,FJohn McGowan-Fazakerley, 32, is
OL,13,Faccused of causing or allowing the
OL,14,Fdeath of 13-month-old Preston Davey,
OL,15,Falong with child cruelty and a sexual
OL,16,Fassault.
OL,18,FHis partner, Jamie Varley, 37, is
OL,19,Faccused of the murder of the child and
OL,20,Fmultiple offences of cruelty and child
OL,21,Fsexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
