PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780430754
OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FBoth men deny a sexual interest in the
OL,7,Fbaby and have pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fall charges.
OL,10,FAnne Whyte KC, defending McGowan-
OL,11,FFazakerley, a graduate with a master's
OL,12,Fdegree who worked as a sales manager
OL,13,Fin finance, asked him about the
OL,14,Faccusation he knew, or should have
OL,15,Fknown, that Preston was at risk from
OL,16,FVarley.
OL,18,FThe defendant replied: "He did
OL,19,Feverything right that I saw.
OL,26,@zD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
