PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780430754
OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,F"He never did anything in my eyesight
OL,7,For when I was at home to make me think
OL,8,For question my leaving this little
OL,9,Fboy, and he's not going to be here any
OL,10,Fmore.
OL,12,F"I trusted Jamie constantly,
OL,13,Findefinitely, there was never a moment
OL,14,FI would not trust him to care for him
OL,15,Fin a way I always saw him to do so."
OL,17,FPreston, a "sweet and bubbly" baby,
OL,18,Fwas adopted by the couple in April
OL,19,F2023.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@dO]yD@LOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
