OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FDuring the four months Preston was
OL,7,Fliving at their Blackpool home it is
OL,8,Falleged he was routinely ill-treated,
OL,9,Fhad indecent images and videos taken
OL,10,Fof him, and was sexually abused and
OL,11,Fphysically assaulted.
OL,13,FPreston had been taken to Blackpool
OL,14,FVictoria Hospital three times already
OL,15,Fbefore his death, when on a final time
OL,16,Fhe was rushed unresponsive to accident
OL,17,Fand emergency by the defendants at
OL,18,Faround 6.30pm on July 27 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
