OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FVarley said he left the child in the
OL,7,Fbath and when he returned two or three
OL,8,Fminutes later he was submerged.
OL,10,FBut a post-mortem examination ruled
OL,11,Fout drowning and found a cause of
OL,12,Fdeath as acute upper airway
OL,13,Fobstruction.
OL,15,FAnd the pathologist found around 40
OL,16,Ftrauma injuries, internally and
OL,17,Fexternally to Preston, including tears
OL,18,Fand lacerations, with "in excess" of
OL,19,F30 bruises across his body.
OL,26,@zD@WOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
