OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FParts of his anatomy were also
OL,7,Fdescribed as "abnormal" with injuries
OL,8,Fconsistent with sexual abuse and
OL,9,F"forcible penetration".
OL,11,FFazakerley-McGowan was asked about
OL,12,FVarley allegedly telling a friend,
OL,13,FJanet Gee, he had "dark thoughts"
OL,14,Fabout the baby by suffocating or
OL,15,Fdrowning him.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@WO]qD@AOUqD@VO]uD@SOUuD@aO]
