OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FMs Whyte continued: "Given what Mr
OL,7,FVarley is alleged to have said about
OL,8,Fthe type of harm, that he disputes,
OL,9,Fand what the prosecution said about
OL,10,Fhis cause of death, how do you feel
OL,11,Fabout the fact that you were not
OL,12,Finformed?"
OL,14,FHe said: "If these conversations
OL,15,Fhappened, I feel quite, it's quite a
OL,16,Fstrong word, disturbed, if those
OL,17,Fconversations happened, why no one has
OL,18,Ftold me about it.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@JO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
