OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,F"I feel heartbroken. She's got my
OL,7,Fnumber. She's a friend. Why on earth
OL,8,Fwould she not pick up that phone and
OL,9,Ftell me or tell somebody that Jamie
OL,10,Fhad that conversation."
OL,12,FThe defendant was then asked about a
OL,13,F14-minute video taken by Varley of
OL,14,FPreston alone in an empty bath to
OL,15,Flearn to 'self-soothe'.
OL,17,FHe said the first he was aware of it
OL,18,Fwas when it was shown to the jury in
OL,19,Fcourt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
