OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FHe said: "Nothing more than just
OL,7,Fshocking and inappropriate and
OL,8,Fpathetic. The video makes me very
OL,9,Fangry. Very angry."
OL,11,FThe defendant was also asked about
OL,12,Fimages from Varley's phone of Preston
OL,13,Fin his cot four days before his death.
OL,15,FThe images stretch over a period of
OL,16,Fthree minutes and 12 seconds, with the
OL,17,Fchild's head and arms over the top
OL,18,Fhorizontal bar of his cot and his neck
OL,19,Fresting on the bar.
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@SO]
