OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FHe told the jury he took only a
OL,7,F"fleeting look" and expected his
OL,8,Fpartner to lay him down while he
OL,9,Fcarried on cooking.
OL,11,FMs Whyte said the prosecution allege
OL,12,Fthe child had been put in that
OL,13,Fposition to be sexually abused by both
OL,14,Fmen.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's sick. It's vile, its
OL,17,Fdisgusting, it's abhorrent, it's
OL,18,Finhuman."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]xD@JOUzD@IO]
