OL,3,C'I trusted partner' co-accused in baby
OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,FMcGowan-Fazakerley said he never
OL,7,Fsuspected Varley and he had never
OL,8,Fsexually assaulted the child.
OL,10,F"That I'm having to have to say those
OL,11,Fwords leave my mouth is ridiculous,"
OL,12,Fhe added.
OL,14,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,15,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,16,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,17,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,18,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,19,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,20,Fone of distributing an
