OL,4,Cmurder trial tells jury
OL,6,Findecent photo of a child, to his co-
OL,7,Faccused, and one of making an indecent
OL,8,Fphoto.
OL,10,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,11,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,12,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,13,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,15,FThe trial was adjourned until
OL,16,FWednesday morning.
